'''乌佩纳维克'''（{{lang-kl|Upernavik}}）是[[格陵兰|格陵兰]]西北部[[阿万纳塔|阿万纳塔]]市镇内的一个城镇，位于一个同名的小岛上。2020年时居民数量为1,092人，为格陵兰第12大的城镇<ref name="stat.gl">{{cite web | url = https://bank.stat.gl/pxweb/en/Greenland/Greenland__BE__BE01__BE0120/BEXST4.PX/ | title = Population in Localities January 1st 1977-2020 | language = en | publisher = StatBank Greenland | accessdate = 2021-01-10 | archive-date = 2021-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210112194352/https://bank.stat.gl/pxweb/en/Greenland/Greenland__BE__BE01__BE0120/BEXST4.PX/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。镇上有{{le|乌佩纳维克博物馆|Upernavik Museum}}。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Runesten_fra_Kingittorsuaq.jpg|thumb]]
1824年，在乌佩纳维克镇外发现了[[青吉托爾蘇阿克盧恩石刻|青吉托爾蘇阿克盧恩石刻]](Kingittorsuaq Runestone)，上面有[[维京人|维京人]]刻的北欧文字<ref>{{cite web |url=https://archive.org/details/RunestenFraKingittorsuaq|title=Kingittorsuaq Runestone|publisher=Nationalmuseet, Danmark}}{{en icon}}</ref>。

